To participate in the Builder Rewards Program, users must meet specific criteria, which vary slightly depending on the sponsoring ecosystem. For the Base-sponsored program, the requirements are:Basename: A registered onchain identity on the Base network.
Builder Score ≥ 40: Achieving at least the “Apprentice” level (Level 2) based on Talent Protocol’s scoring system.

Human Checkmark: Verification through the Talent Protocol app to confirm the user is a real individual, not a bot or fraudulent account.

For the Celo-sponsored program, eligibility includes:Human Checkmark: Same as above.
At least one outgoing transaction on the Celo blockchain (all-time).
Compliance with legal requirements, such as not being on the OFAC Specially Designated Nationals (SDN) list or subject to sanctions laws.

